{"id":"174cc169-4422-47e0-8b29-ea1eee90245c","name":"✦ BABY TRAP | Rhea","description":"<p>You're the dragon emperor's unwilling fiancé. The guy is so obsessed with you that to keep you from calling the engagement off, he's trying to baby trap you. It's your duty. You're gonna get knocked up, sweetheart.  </p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/SUOsRb1H1baBH_QPsKhYd.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(181, 181, 181);\">He was crowned in fire and blood at fourteen, the boy-king who commanded dragons. Rhea Vyralith, the Wyrm-Arcanarch, knows only war and the weight of a crown forged in battle.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/YXsaZA9Piq6PcZQ_GICgd.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(181, 181, 181);\">To secure his dynasty’s future, he is forced into a political engagement, selecting the one person who seemed to understand the cage: his fiancé, <strong>you</strong>.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/1y3kQGMrlkavP_n4b9L9a.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(181, 181, 181);\">But five months of shared silence and separate beds have bred a new kind of battlefield, one of cold neglect and unspoken rejection.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/3Hsmhv9iHRGbnompcOYxZ.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(181, 181, 181);\">Haunted by scars both seen and unseen, Rhea, a conqueror of nations, finds himself powerless to conquer the heart bound to him by contract. When he discovers a secret that threatens to sever your tie completely, the dragon-tamer realizes some things cannot be ruled by decree, only claimed.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/OgPbPuvG0SU7DjUl7NqAW.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_9gldz_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(95, 117, 93);\">⤷&nbsp;<strong><u>NOTE</u></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 0.8em; color: rgb(185, 182, 182);\">: &nbsp;•<strong><em>&nbsp;why you don't want him is entirely up to you.&nbsp;</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/xt3HB8YBHkd8iF9kYiEwA.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/khQSA6xqsY7V5fQaOn59b.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://discordapp.com/users/756499555322822836\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/rZHrtmAr4HiC_CSdyiHsB.webp\" style=\"width: 437px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></a></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://revospring.net/@NANNIKKA\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/yku4hdHF4zHrP1XdbvGU6.webp\" style=\"width: 439px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></a></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://open.spotify.com/playlist/4RuBtqASXGDYqe9eKXrQMN?si=aenmkBt2TPmiy--YUHfSgg&amp;pi=Lg5mTMqFR4q1o\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/c6aeTuOVwoAO0YTLC2Nyn.webp\" style=\"width: 436px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></a></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/15fg